                            <comment id="14135403" author="shalinmangar" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 13:16:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think, at a minimum, we should reduce the max wait time of 600 seconds (10 minutes).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14135406" author="shalinmangar" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 13:19:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A workaround for people who are affected is to call core reload or collection reload to force restart the recovery process.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14135608" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 15:39:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agreed - lets drop the max retry time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14180191" author="shalinmangar" created="Wed, 22 Oct 2014 17:15:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch sets max retry wait time to 1 minute instead of 10 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
